{"tid":1816510,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新城巿廣場公共空間被封閉 疑違反地契","createTime":"2020-01-08T09:40:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T11:05:46.000Z","uid":10540,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a662f9d882daac1e1dd9e18fa1d6af9f5d43f587","tid":1816510,"uid":10540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DdfqW2u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDdfqW2u.jpg&h=849dd2b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼有市民發現新城巿廣場封鎖多個往戶外平台的樓梯後，有市民發現管理公司今日在5樓和7樓用圍板或安裝警報系統封鎖往平台花園公共空間的出入口，變相市民失去享用公共空間的權利。沙田區專頁已就問題向地政處投訴，有待回覆。亦希望沙田區的區議員能加強監察商場運作。<br />\n<br />\n根據地政總署的地契規定，寫明於新城市廣場一期個別樓層內，需要預留地方作公共空間，包括3、5、7及9樓的綠化天台。開放時間應為每天上午7時至晚上10時。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>沙田地政處</strong><br />\n辦公室電話：2158 4700<br />\n電郵：gendlost@landsd.gov.hk"},{"pid":"f1038ff546c5fe5bf5c3a88eae815fd40358c621","tid":1816510,"uid":173207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd3462bec6f4a35574f29c86cd1899de12aad7fd","tid":1816510,"uid":113155,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:47:29.000Z","msg":"自從區選後，發現議員原來可以做咁多嘢。<br />\n真係對唔住，以前係我衰，豬到連選民都冇做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adb61e3107746fec8127882dddfcc519cd9afd9","tid":1816510,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:53:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c555db4f4812d00586ae307819b172ada7d77067","tid":1816510,"uid":19005,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:58:32.000Z","msg":"平台花園真係唔好搞  <br />\n多咗一個放鬆選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96fc6b6265a6752af73cde6c1625ba1e957f2142","tid":1816510,"uid":2267,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cd3462bec6f4a35574f29c86cd1899de12aad7fd","tid":1816510,"uid":113155,"like":11,"dislike":3,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:47:29.000Z","m